# workoutName

**Instance Property**

The name of the workout.

## Declaration

```swift
@NSCopying var workoutName: INSpeakableString? { get }
```

## Discussion

If the user canceled a specific workout, this property contains the name of that workout. The workout name can be user-specified, a workout name defined in your app’s global vocabulary file, or a custom workout name spoken by the user.
